21:23.408 --> 21:27.203
[groans, sighs]

21:27.203 --> 21:28.872
What now, sir?

21:28.872 --> 21:30.290
Now?

21:30.290 --> 21:32.375
I'm still dealing
with her face.

21:32.375 --> 21:37.547
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21:37.547 --> 21:40.216
[person grunts]

21:40.216 --> 21:42.469
[gunshot]

21:42.469 --> 21:44.304
- [objects clatter]
- Strike.

21:44.304 --> 21:48.099
Let's think about this.
What do we have going for us?

21:48.099 --> 21:51.644
Okay, for starters,
the killers in that hotel--

21:51.644 --> 21:53.146
they're men and women, right?

21:53.146 --> 21:54.647
They bleed just like we do.

21:54.647 --> 21:57.192
They also
won't be expecting us, right?

21:57.192 --> 21:59.361
Because no one's ever made
a run at The Continental.

21:59.361 --> 22:01.112
Yeah, because
it's fucking insane.

22:01.112 --> 22:03.823
We're gonna need more fingers
to pull all these triggers.

22:03.823 --> 22:05.825
Okay, do you have
any other military friends?

22:05.825 --> 22:07.827
Not that I'd bring in
on this.

22:07.827 --> 22:09.871
Most of those guys are just
trying to find their way back.

22:09.871 --> 22:11.623
Those willing to get
their hands this dirty,

22:11.623 --> 22:13.041
