22:13.041 --> 22:15.085
Gonna be a bitch
trying to find somebody

22:15.085 --> 22:16.503
not already in his pocket.

22:16.503 --> 22:18.672
Well, there
has to be somebody.

22:18.672 --> 22:21.549
- Well, there is Gene.
- Jenkins?

22:21.549 --> 22:23.885
- Dad's old friend?
- Yeah.

22:23.885 --> 22:26.346
At one time, he even had a
corner room at The Continental.

22:26.346 --> 22:29.140
Okay.
It's a good start.

22:30.934 --> 22:33.687
Hey, Lou, where's your head at
with all this?

22:33.687 --> 22:36.064
I'll help.
God knows you're gonna need it.

22:36.064 --> 22:37.816
But I won't be pulling
any triggers,

22:37.816 --> 22:40.819
and I will not storm
the castle.

22:40.819 --> 22:42.821
[gun cocks]
What?

22:44.739 --> 22:47.534
There's always Mazie.
She's no fan of Cormac.

22:47.534 --> 22:49.536
Yeah, she bought
from us last year,

22:49.536 --> 22:51.371
or at least I think she did.

22:51.371 --> 22:52.706
Never met her face-to-face.

22:52.706 --> 22:54.708
Runs an operation
out the Bowery.

22:54.708 --> 22:57.210
Nobody knows exactly what
it is or who works for her.

22:57.210 --> 23:00.005
They talk about it like
it's the army of the unseen,

23:00.005 --> 23:04.342
like she's the queenpin
of the criminals.

23:04.342 --> 23:07.053
I mean, that--that's--that's
the nickname I gave her,

23:07.053 --> 23:09.222
but she's definitely
a competitor of Cormac.

23:09.222 --> 23:10.932
I don't understand.
Why hasn't he snuffed her out?

23:10.932 --> 23:12.600
Well, it's not easy
to snuff something out

23:12.600 --> 23:14.269
when you don't know
what you're snuffing.

23:14.269 --> 23:16.896
Mazie's group doesn't ally
itself with outsiders.

23:16.896 --> 23:18.940
Anybody not from the Bowery
can forget it.

23:18.940 --> 23:21.609
Well, I'll take my chances.
Where in the Bowery?

23:21.609 --> 23:23.570
We could tell you
where we made the drop,

23:23.570 --> 23:25.572
but adjust your expectations.

23:25.572 --> 23:29.075
