you wanted replaced.

26:14.574 --> 26:17.369
Oh.
Straight to business.

26:17.369 --> 26:18.995
How fun.

26:25.627 --> 26:27.087
What?

26:27.087 --> 26:30.757
There's nothing
wrong with it.

26:30.757 --> 26:33.301
Works perfectly.

26:33.301 --> 26:35.470
No, there's definitely
something wrong

26:35.470 --> 26:36.763
with that sight.

26:36.763 --> 26:38.598
That's not in question here,

26:38.598 --> 26:41.351
although I'm not
entirely certain what is.

26:43.186 --> 26:45.397
