26:45.397 --> 26:47.357
What's the serial number?

26:50.985 --> 26:54.739
Really, Miles,
a pop quiz?

26:54.739 --> 26:56.783
I'll wait for finals.

27:01.121 --> 27:03.873
So how's Lou doing these days?

27:03.873 --> 27:05.875
[bottle thuds on counter]

27:05.875 --> 27:08.586
- She's doing okay.
- Oh, really?

27:08.586 --> 27:12.966
Not still grieving the, uh,
absence of your father?

27:12.966 --> 27:14.968
I wouldn't say she's over it.

27:14.968 --> 27:17.470
Well, maybe the truth
would help in that regard--

27:17.470 --> 27:18.972
parts of it, anyway.

27:18.972 --> 27:20.765
I'm not here to talk
about all that, Gene.

27:20.765 --> 27:23.727
So you just dropped in to
convince a retiree to retire.

27:23.727 --> 27:25.478
- You're not retired.
- Oh, please.

27:25.478 --> 27:26.813
Why not find yourself a lady?

27:26.813 --> 27:28.356
Enjoy your golden years.

27:28.356 --> 27:29.691
And do what...

27:29.691 --> 27:31.317
regale her
with tales of my youth,

27:31.317 --> 27:35.613
when I could liquefy
a man's brains at 350 yards?

27:35.613 --> 27:38.950
What kind of lady
would that attract?

27:38.950 --> 27:42.787
No, no, I think I'll stick
to the solitary life.

27:42.787 --> 27:44.247
Suit yourself.

27:47.375 --> 27:49.544
Good to see you, Gene.

27:49.544 --> 27:50.920
What is going on with you?

27:50.920 --> 27:53.214
- What are you talking about?
- Come on.

27:53.214 --> 27:56.384
I've known you since before
you could poop on the potty.

27:56.384 --> 27:58.386
Something's brewing.

27:58.386 --> 28:00.138
It's not something
I can talk about, Gene.

28:00.138 --> 28:03.558
What's that,
The Continental?

28:03.558 --> 28:08.229
Word on the street--
some young'uns in trouble.

28:08.229 --> 28:10.607
We're trying to put together
a crew.

28:10.607 --> 28:12.859
