Crazy?

28:16.863 --> 28:20.033
Suicidal or not...

28:20.033 --> 28:23.244
yours is a righteous cause.

28:23.244 --> 28:27.123
If anyone ever deserved
to be eliminated...

28:28.708 --> 28:30.960
