30:35.752 --> 30:37.003
Please.

30:37.003 --> 30:39.381
We don't serve
your kind here.

30:39.381 --> 30:40.840
That's good,

30:40.840 --> 30:42.884
because I don't eat my kind.

30:42.884 --> 30:44.594
[grunts]

30:44.594 --> 30:46.096
