30:46.096 --> 30:48.264
Put your knife down,
pretty boy.

30:49.724 --> 30:51.226
My apologies.

30:51.226 --> 30:54.396
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

30:54.396 --> 31:01.403
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:14.749 --> 31:16.376
[knife clatters on plate]

31:16.376 --> 31:18.920
You must be the woman
I'm looking for.

31:18.920 --> 31:20.880
And you must be
the son of a bitch

31:20.880 --> 31:23.258
everyone's looking for.

